headline: Nierenberg Loads Up On Lyft Stock With 771,000 Shares Bought
summary: Lyft stake now comprises 7.65% of fund AUM, ranking as the fund's 4th-largest holding.

headline: EQT Future to acquire a majority stake in DESOTEC, a leader in circular mobile filtration solutions
summary: EQT is pleased to announce that the EQT Future fund (or "EQT") has agreed to acquire a majority stake in DESOTEC (the "Company"), a leader in circular mobile filtration solutions, from private equity funds managed by Blackstone, which will remain a minority investor.
